<bibRefCitation author="Marijnissen, S. &amp; Schram, F. &amp; Cumberlidge, N. &amp; Michel, A. E." box="[837,1135,684,710]" pageId="54" pagination="513 - 532" refId="ref41787" refString="Marijnissen, S., Schram, F., Cumberlidge, N. &amp; Michel, A. E. (2004) Two new species of Platythelphusa A. Milne-Edwards, 1887 (Decapoda, Potamoidea, Platythelphusidae) and comments on the taxonomic position of P. denticulata Capart, 1952 from Lake Tanganyika, East Africa. Crustaceana 77 (5), 513 - 532." type="journal article" year="2004">
